Get separation range

1 epoch = 4 seconds recording for 4 days 6h SD 3rd day Light-Dark cycle

# 900 epochs = 1h
Hours<-c()
for (i in seq(1,24)){Hours<-c(Hours,rep(i,900))}
Hours<-rep(Hours,4)

# Days
Days<-c()
for (i in seq(1,4)){Days<-c(Days,rep(i,21600))}

# Light Dark cycle by 6h 
LD<-c()
for (i in c("L1","L2","D1","D2")){LD<-c(LD,rep(i,5400))}
LD<-rep(LD,4)
LD[Days==3 & LD == "L1"]<-"L1SD" # SD

Read BXD Data

BXDmdata<-matrix(ncol=0,nrow=8*10800)
BXDStrain<-c()
for (mouse in c(WithVariant,WithoutVariant)){
   mouseshort<-gsub("BXD","",mouse)
   fi<-list.files("BXD_Data/",paste("^",mouseshort,sep=""))
   for (f in fi){
      BXDStrain<-c(BXDStrain,mouse)
      data<-as.character(read.table(paste("BXD_Data/",f,sep=""))$V1)
      BXDmdata<-cbind(BXDmdata,data)
      colnames(BXDmdata)[ncol(BXDmdata)]<-f
   }
}

BXDDBF1mdata<-matrix(ncol=0,nrow=8*10800)

Count NREM sleep event

NREMcount<-function(mdata,mouse){
  tmpdata<-as.character(mdata[,mouse])
  nbNREM<-0
  if ("n" %in% names(table(tmpdata))){nbNREM<-table(tmpdata)["n"]}
  nb2<-0
  if ("2" %in% names(table(tmpdata))){nb2<-table(tmpdata)["2"]}
  result<-(nbNREM+nb2)/15
  #result<-(nbNREM)/15
  return(result)
}

GetGain<-function(interval,ref="Own"){
  if (interval == "12-24"){
    seqData<-Days==3 & (LD == "D1" | LD == "D2")
    seqRefB1<-Days==1 & (LD == "D1" | LD == "D2")
    seqRefB2<-Days==2 & (LD == "D1" | LD == "D2")
  } 
  
  if (interval == "12-24-Day4"){
    seqData<-Days==4 & (LD == "D1" | LD == "D2")
    seqRefB1<-Days==1 & (LD == "D1" | LD == "D2")
    seqRefB2<-Days==2 & (LD == "D1" | LD == "D2")
  }
  
  if (interval == "12-18"){
    seqData<-Days==3 & LD == "D1"
    seqRefB1<-Days==1 & LD == "D1"
    seqRefB2<-Days==2 & LD == "D1"
  } 
  
  if (interval == "12-18-Day4"){
    seqData<-Days==4 & LD == "D1"
    seqRefB1<-Days==1 & LD == "D1"
    seqRefB2<-Days==2 & LD == "D1"
  } 
  
  if (interval == "18-24"){
    seqData<-Days==3 & LD == "D2"
    seqRefB1<-Days==1 & LD == "D2"
    seqRefB2<-Days==2 & LD == "D2"
  } 
  if (interval == "18-24-Day4"){
    seqData<-Days==4 & LD == "D2"
    seqRefB1<-Days==1 & LD == "D2"
    seqRefB2<-Days==2 & LD == "D2"
  } 
  
  if (interval == "24h"){
    seqData<-(Days==3 & (LD == "D2" | LD == "D1" | LD == "L2")) | (Days==4 & (LD == "L1"))
    seqRefB1<-Days==1
    seqRefB2<-Days==2
  } 
  
  if (interval == "24h-Day4"){
    seqData<-Days==4
    seqRefB1<-Days==1
    seqRefB2<-Days==2
  } 
    
  mdatafilt<-mdata[seqData,]
  BXDDBF1mdatafilt<-BXDDBF1mdata[seqData ,]
  BXDmdatafilt<-BXDmdata[seqData,]
  mdatafilt_B1<-mdata[seqRefB1,]
  mdatafilt_B2<-mdata[seqRefB2,]
  BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B1<-BXDDBF1mdata[seqRefB1 ,]
  BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B2<-BXDDBF1mdata[seqRefB2 ,]
  BXDmdatafilt_B1<-BXDmdata[seqRefB1,]
  BXDmdatafilt_B2<-BXDmdata[seqRefB2,]
  
  # C57BL6
  BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain<-c()
  BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  for (i in BXDBL6){
    BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain<-c(BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain,NREMcount(mdatafilt,i))
    BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1<-c(BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B1,i))
    BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2<-c(BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B2,i))
  }
  BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_Ref<-(BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1+BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2)/2
  #print("C57 OK ")
  
  BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain<-c()
  BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  i<-"DBA"
  for (j in which(BXDDBF1Strain==i)){
    BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain<-c(BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
    BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B1<-c(BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B1,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
    BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B2<-c(BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B2,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
  }
  BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_Ref<-(BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B1+BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_B2)/2 
  #print("DBA OK ")
  
  BXD_DBF1_NREMGain<-c()
  BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  i<-"DBF"
  for (j in which(BXDDBF1Strain==i)){
    BXD_DBF1_NREMGain<-c(BXD_DBF1_NREMGain,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
    BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B1<-c(BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B1,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
    BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B2<-c(BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B2,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
  }
  BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_Ref<-(BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B1+BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_B2)/2 
  #print("DB OK ")
  
  BXD_BDF1_NREMGain<-c()
  BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  i<-"BDF"
  for (j in which(BXDDBF1Strain==i)){
    BXD_BDF1_NREMGain<-c(BXD_BDF1_NREMGain,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
    BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B1<-c(BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B1,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
    BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B2<-c(BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(BXDDBF1mdatafilt_B2,colnames(BXDDBF1mdata)[j]))
  }
  BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_Ref<-(BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B1+BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_B2)/2 
  #print("BD OK ")
  
  BXD_B6allel_NREMGain<-c()
  BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  for (i in WithoutVariant){
    tmpdata<-c()
    tmpdata_b1<-c()
    tmpdata_b2<-c()
    for (j in which(BXDStrain==i)){
      tmpdata<-c(tmpdata,NREMcount(BXDmdatafilt,colnames(BXDmdatafilt)[j]))
      tmpdata_b1<-c(tmpdata_b1,NREMcount(BXDmdatafilt_B1,colnames(BXDmdatafilt_B1)[j]))
      tmpdata_b2<-c(tmpdata_b2,NREMcount(BXDmdatafilt_B2,colnames(BXDmdatafilt_B2)[j]))
    }
    BXD_B6allel_NREMGain<-c(BXD_B6allel_NREMGain,mean(tmpdata))
    BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B1<-c(BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B1,mean(tmpdata_b1))
    BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B2<-c(BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B2,mean(tmpdata_b2))
  }
  BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_Ref<-(BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B1+BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_B2)/2 
  #print("B6All OK ")
  
  
  BXD_D2allel_NREMGain<-c()
  BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  for (i in WithVariant){
    tmpdata<-c()
    tmpdata_b1<-c()
    tmpdata_b2<-c()
    for (j in which(BXDStrain==i)){
      tmpdata<-c(tmpdata,NREMcount(BXDmdatafilt,colnames(BXDmdatafilt)[j]))
      tmpdata_b1<-c(tmpdata_b1,NREMcount(BXDmdatafilt_B1,colnames(BXDmdatafilt_B1)[j]))
      tmpdata_b2<-c(tmpdata_b2,NREMcount(BXDmdatafilt_B2,colnames(BXDmdatafilt_B2)[j]))
    }
    BXD_D2allel_NREMGain<-c(BXD_D2allel_NREMGain,mean(tmpdata))
    BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B1<-c(BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B1,mean(tmpdata_b1))
    BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B2<-c(BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B2,mean(tmpdata_b2))
  }
  BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_Ref<-(BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B1+BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_B2)/2 
  #print("D2all OK ")
  
  ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain<-c()
  ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  for (i in miceWTACOT){
    ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain<-c(ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain,NREMcount(mdatafilt,i))
    ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1<-c(ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B1,i))
    ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2<-c(ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B2,i))
  }
  ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_Ref<-(ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B1+ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_B2)/2
  #print("WT OK ")
  
  ACOT_KO_NREMGain<-c()
  ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  for (i in miceKO){
    ACOT_KO_NREMGain<-c(ACOT_KO_NREMGain,NREMcount(mdatafilt,i))
    ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B1<-c(ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B1,i))
    ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B2<-c(ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B2,i))
  }
  ACOT_KO_NREMGain_Ref<-(ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B1+ACOT_KO_NREMGain_B2)/2
  #print("KO OK ")
  
  
  ACOT_HT_NREMGain<-c()
  ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B1<-c()
  ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B2<-c()
  for (i in miceHT){
    ACOT_HT_NREMGain<-c(ACOT_HT_NREMGain,NREMcount(mdatafilt,i))
    ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B1<-c(ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B1,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B1,i))
    ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B2<-c(ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B2,NREMcount(mdatafilt_B2,i))
  }
  ACOT_HT_NREMGain_Ref<-(ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B1+ACOT_HT_NREMGain_B2)/2
  #print("HT OK ")
  
  par(mar=c(10,3,3,3))
  
  if (ref == "All"){
      RefAll<-mean(c(BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_Ref,BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain_Ref,BXD_B6allel_NREMGain_Ref,BXD_D2allel_NREMGain_Ref,BXD_BDF1_NREMGain_Ref,BXD_DBF1_NREMGain_Ref,ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain_Ref,ACOT_KO_NREMGain_Ref,ACOT_HT_NREMGain_Ref))
      GainValue<-list("C57BL/6J"=BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain-RefAll,
                 "DBA/2J"=BXD_DBA2J_NREMGain-RefAll,

                 "Acot11 +/+"=ACOT_C57BL6_NREMGain-RefAll,

  }
  
  
  if (ref=="Own"){
    
      GainValue<-list("C57BL/6J"=BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain-BXD_C57BL6_NREMGain_Ref,

}

plot_Barplot<-function(resultats){
  
  MeansValue<-c()
  for (i in names(resultats)){
    MeansValue<-c(MeansValue,mean(resultats[[i]]))
  }
  names(MeansValue)<-names(resultats)
  
  colorsBarplot<-c(rgb(0,0,0,1),
                   rgb(0.7,0.5,0.3,1),
                   rgb(0.5,0.5,0.5,0.8),
                   rgb(0.85,0.67,0.44,0.8),
                   rgb(1,1,1,1),rgb(1,1,1,1),
                   rgb(0,0,0,0.75),
                   rgb(1,0.2,0.2,1),
                   rgb(1,0.2,0.2,1))
  
  den<-c(-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,20)
  
  if (min(MeansValue)<0){
      bar<-barplot(height=MeansValue,
          las=2,ylim=c(min(MeansValue)-5,max(MeansValue)+15),ylab="NREM gain [min]",col=colorsBarplot,density = den)
  }else{
      bar<-barplot(height=MeansValue,
          las=2,ylim=c(0,max(MeansValue)+15),ylab="NREM gain [min]",col=colorsBarplot,density = den)
  }

  # std.error
  library(plotrix)
  StdErrors<-c()
  for (i in names(resultats)){
    StdErrors<-c(StdErrors,std.error(resultats[[i]]))
  }
  names(StdErrors)<-names(resultats)
  
  epsilon<-0.02
  for (i in 1:length(names(resultats))){
        up = MeansValue[i] + StdErrors[i]
        low = MeansValue[i] - StdErrors[i]
        segments(bar[i,1],low , bar[i,1], up)
        segments(bar[i,1]-epsilon, up , bar[i,1]+epsilon, up)
        segments(bar[i,1]-epsilon, low , bar[i,1]+epsilon, low) 
  }
  
}


plot_Barplot2<-function(resultats,NOF1=F){
  
  par(mar=c(10,5,3,3))
  
  if (NOF1==F){
    resultats[[5]]<-c(resultats$BDF1,resultats$DBF1)
    resultats<-resultats[-6]
    names(resultats)[5]<-"F1" 
  } else {
    resultats<-resultats[-c(5,6)]
  }
  
  MeansValue<-c()
  for (i in names(resultats)){
    MeansValue<-c(MeansValue,mean(resultats[[i]]))
  }
  names(MeansValue)<-names(resultats)
  
  Acot_BXDSpace<-1.5
  NormalSpace<-.15
  
  if (NOF1==F){
    colorsBarplot<-c(rgb(0,0,0,1),
                   rgb(0.7,0.5,0.3,1),
                   rgb(0.5,0.5,0.5,0.8),
                   rgb(0.85,0.67,0.44,0.8),
                   rgb(1,1,1,1),
                   rgb(0,0,0,0.75),
                   rgb(1,0.2,0.2,1),
                   rgb(1,0.2,0.2,1))
  
    den<-c(-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,20)
    space<-c(NormalSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace,Acot_BXDSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace)
  } else {
    colorsBarplot<-c(rgb(0,0,0,1),
                   rgb(0.7,0.5,0.3,1),
                   rgb(0.5,0.5,0.5,0.8),
                   rgb(0.85,0.67,0.44,0.8),
                   rgb(0,0,0,0.75),
                   rgb(1,0.2,0.2,1),
                   rgb(1,0.2,0.2,1))
  
    den<-c(-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,-1,20)
    space<-c(NormalSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace,Acot_BXDSpace,NormalSpace,NormalSpace)
  }
  
  if (min(MeansValue)<0){
      bar<-barplot(height=MeansValue,
          las=2,ylim=c(min(MeansValue)-20,max(MeansValue)+15),ylab="NREM gain [min]",col=colorsBarplot,density = den,
          space=space)
  }else{
      bar<-barplot(height=MeansValue,
          las=2,ylim=c(0,max(MeansValue)+20),ylab="NREM gain [min]",col=colorsBarplot,density = den,
          space=space)
  }
  
  # std.error
  library(plotrix)
  StdErrors<-c()
  for (i in names(resultats)){
    StdErrors<-c(StdErrors,std.error(resultats[[i]]))
  }
  names(StdErrors)<-names(resultats)
  
  epsilon<-0.02
  for (i in 1:length(names(resultats))){
        up = MeansValue[i] + StdErrors[i]
        low = MeansValue[i] - StdErrors[i]
        segments(bar[i,1],low , bar[i,1], up)
        segments(bar[i,1]-epsilon, up , bar[i,1]+epsilon, up)
        segments(bar[i,1]-epsilon, low , bar[i,1]+epsilon, low) 
  }
  
  h1<-max(MeansValue[c("Acot11 +/+","Acot11 -/-")])+max(StdErrors[c("Acot11 +/+","Acot11 -/-")]+2)
  h2<-max(MeansValue[c("Acot11 +/+","Acot11 +/-")])+max(StdErrors[c("Acot11 +/+","Acot11 +/-")]+3)
  h3<-max(MeansValue[c("BXD-B6 Allele","BXD-D2 Allele")])+max(StdErrors[c("BXD-B6 Allele","BXD-D2 Allele")]+2)
  rownames(bar)<-names(MeansValue)
  segments(bar["Acot11 +/+",1],h1,bar["Acot11 -/-",1],h1)
  segments(bar["Acot11 +/+",1],h2,bar["Acot11 +/-",1],h2)
  segments(bar["BXD-B6 Allele",1],h3,bar["BXD-D2 Allele",1],h3)
  
  t1<-t.test(resultats$`Acot11 +/+`,resultats$`Acot11 -/-`)$p.value
  t2<-t.test(resultats$`Acot11 +/+`,resultats$`Acot11 +/-`)$p.value
  t3<-t.test(resultats$`BXD-B6 Allele`,resultats$`BXD-D2 Allele`)$p.value
  
  padj<-p.adjust(c(t1,t2,t3),method="fdr")
  t1<-padj[1]
  t2<-padj[2]
  t3<-padj[3]
  pvals<-c(t1,t2,t3)
  stars<-StarPval(pvals)
  
  
  text(x=(bar["Acot11 +/+",1]+bar["Acot11 -/-",1])/2,y=h1+2,stars[[1]][1],col="red",cex=1.5)
  text(x=(bar["Acot11 +/+",1]+bar["Acot11 +/-",1])/2,y=h2+2,stars[[2]][1],col="red",cex=1.5)
  text(x=(bar["BXD-B6 Allele",1]+bar["BXD-D2 Allele",1])/2,y=h3+2,stars[[3]][1],col="red",cex=1.5)

  
}

StarPval<-function(pvals){
  stars<-as.list(pvals)
  i<-3
  for (i in 1:length(pvals)){
    tt<-pvals[[i]]
    if (tt<0.0001){stars[[i]]<-'****'
    }else if (tt<0.001){stars[[i]]<-'***'
    }else if (tt<0.01){stars[[i]]<-'**'
    }else if (tt<0.05){stars[[i]]<-'*'
    }else{stars[[i]]<-'ns'}
  }
  return(stars)
}

In order to control for Acot11 effect on NREM sleep gain, we contrasted global Acot11 KO and heterozygous mice (REF Zhang et al. 2012 ?) with their corresponding C57BL6(N?J?) wild-type background using same sleep deprivation design used for BXD lines. While for the BXD lines, the effect of Acot11 was detected with the strongest effect on the first 6h of the dark phase [ZT:12-18] where most sleep compensation occured, we did not detect a significant change of NREM gain for Acot11 KO in this specific interval. However, over the whole dark period and specifically during the second 6h interval of the dark phase [ZT:18-24], a lower gain of NREM sleep was observed for Acot11 KO and HT compared to WT. In this interval, WT mice gained 31.2 minutes of NREM sleep while Acot11 KO gained only -0.4 minutes of NREM sleep (P.value = 0.0023). It was intersting to notice that most NREM sleep gain for C57BL/6J substrain occured during the first hours of the dark (ZT:12-18: 37.7 min, ZT:18-24: 13.3 min), while C57BL6(N?) mice compensated also during the second interval (ZT:12-18: 45.7 min, ZT:18-24: 31.2 min), where we detected Acot11 effect. Over the whole dark period [ZT:12-24], Acot11 KO gained 49.1 minutes of NREM sleep while WT mice gained 76.9 minutes (P.value = 0.0054). This difference over the whole dark period could also be observed for the BXD. (Figure barplot). The difference of genetic background used between BXD and Acot11 KO, and the interaction with DBA/2J variation within BXD lines, can explain the different time phase effect of Acot11 that we observe on NREM sleep compensation in the dark.
